Combine oil with Knorr(R) Beef flavor Bouillon Cube in small cup, mashing with fork until blended; rub over steak. Cook steak in large nonstick skillet over medium-high heat until desired doneness. Remove steak and set aside. Prepare Knorr(R) Menu Flavors Rice Sides(TM) - Asian BBQ in same skillet according to package directions. Meanwhile, combine carrot, snow peas, green onions and lime juice in medium bowl; set aside. Thinly slice steak. Evenly divide rice between tortillas. Top with steak, then vegetable mixture.